      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:47:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国在工业界抗议下提高北海石油和天然气税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-raises-north-sea-oil-gas-taxes-amid-protest-from-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新政府履行承诺，加强对北海石油和天然气生产商的税收制度，增加暴利税并取消一些投资津贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-raises-north-sea-oil-gas-taxes-amid-protest-from-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:22:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉在选举后镇压中拘留反对派人士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/venezuela-apprehends-opposition-figure-amid-election-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉政府正在全面镇压任何抵抗总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗自我宣布的胜利的行为，并于周二宣布逮捕 749 人，并拘留了著名反对派人物弗雷迪·苏佩拉诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/venezuela-apprehends-opposition-figure-amid-election-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
